[Amit Varma]: Welcome back to the scene in the unseen we are chatting with the multifaceted Deepak

01:11:38.360 --> 01:11:39.360
[Amit Varma]: Sinha.

01:11:39.360 --> 01:11:42.920
[Amit Varma]: You know, people are as Isaiah Berlin once said, foxes are hedgehogs.

01:11:42.920 --> 01:11:47.080
[Amit Varma]: You know, foxes who you know, know a little bit of a vast variety of subjects and hedgehogs

